latestIgtvVideos.title: How to apply lipstick perfectly and long lasting ✌️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Many of you ask about long lasting lipsticks so here I am telling some hacks to make your lips looking flawless 

The steps to the pout perfect lips are here

1 Exfoliation is the first step to get rid of chapped lips
Here i am using peach lip scrub from @justherbsindia 

2 moisturising your lips after Exfoliation is mandatory 
I am using primer stick by @bellavoste before applying my lipstick 

3 line your lips with a suitable lip liner here i am using myglamm lit lip liner pencil by @myglamm 

4 fill it with shade of your choice
I used @wetnwildindia megalast catsuit matte liquid lipstick (shade : Give me mocha)

5 Gave a glossy tint using lip loss by @nykaabeauty (shade Name drop 06)
